<Location xmlns="http://hl7.org/fhir">
  <id value="location02"/>
  <meta>
    <profile
             value="http://hl7.org/fhir/us/qicore/StructureDefinition/qicore-location"/>
  </meta>
  <text>
    <status value="generated"/>
    <div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><p><b>Generated Narrative with Details</b></p><p><b>id</b>: location02</p><p><b>meta</b>: </p><p><b>name</b>: DaVinciClinic02</p><p><b>address</b>: 21 W. Atlantic Street Burlington NJ 08873 USA </p></div>
  </text>
  <name value="DaVinciClinic02"/>
  <address>
    <line value="21 W. Atlantic Street"/>
    <city value="Burlington"/>
    <state value="NJ"/>
    <postalCode value="08873"/>
    <country value="USA"/>
  </address>
</Location>
